<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.10.10">
<l>paṇṭumu ṉēṉa mākiyaṉ ṟorukāl pāriṭan teyiṟṟiṉil koṇṭu</l>
<l>teṇṭirai varuṭap pāṟkaṭal tuyiṉṟa tiruveḷḷi yaṅkuṭi yāṉai</l>
<l>vaṇṭaṟai cōlai maṅkaiyar talaivaṉ māṉavēl kaliyaṉvā yolikaḷ</l>
<l>koṇṭivai pāṭun tavamuṭai yārka ḷāḷvarik kuraikaṭa lulakē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who have [merit gained from] austerities who sing these [songs],</l>
<l rend="indent">learning the poems of Kaliyaṉ with a proud spear,</l>
<l>Chief of those of Maṅkai, with groves where bees hum,</l>
<l rend="indent">about the one of Tiruveḷḷiyaṅkuṭi,</l>
<l>Who sleeps on the Sea of Milk as clear waves stroke [him],</l>
<l rend="indent">having that day long ago,</l>
<l>Previously as a boar, dug the earth once, taking [it] on its tusks,</l>
<l rend="indent">they will rule this world with roaring seas.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
